      "content": "but i literally can't afford a hospital visit right now i'm super short on cash. if i just take a bunch of paracetamol and some of my friend's leftover antibiotics maybe it will clear up on its own? i just need the pain to stop so i can sleep. is there any way to just manage it at home for tonight?",
